  "title": "TCM Receptionist and Admin",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Perform general receptionist and administrative duties</li><li>Greet customers and arrange appointment bookings</li><li>Answer phone calls / WhatsApp messages / basic customer service responses</li><li>Simple administrative and front desk duties</li><li>Assist customers with understanding of services</li><li>Assist with communication and translation to customer</li></ul></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Detail-oriented, patient and customer-service minded</li><li>Good communication skills with a friendly attitude</li><li>Able to handle front desk / reception duties</li><li>Prior experience in front desk / administration / customer service is preferred</li><li>Able to communicate in English and Chinese</li></ul></p><p><strong>Other Info:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Commission payable</li><li>Growth opportunities</li></ul><p>All applications will be treated confidentially.</p><p>By submitting your résumé to us, you will be deemed to have consented to us disclosing your personal information to prospective employers for their consideration.</p><p>EA Licence No.: 24C2507</p></p>",
